          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "narration",
          "speaker": null,
          "text": "<ff><e5>1<f1>K<63><aa>P<a8>2q<ff><58>2<ae>1mI<60>A<85><f1>:p<e1><e1>4o<e1><e1>4<f1>Xo<e1><e1><e1>4p<e1><e1><e1>4<f1>XzJ<4b><db>O <PRAYER>Father<e2>6,<PRAYER> abandon not Your wayward<f8>children of Ivalice<e2>6,<PRAYER> but deliver us from our<f8>sins<e2>6,<PRAYER> that we might know salvation<e2>K.<e2>1",
          "raw_byte_range": [
            22649,
            22855
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "speaker",
          "speaker": "Knight",
          "text": "<SPEAKER>Knight<f8><e3>Lady Ovelia, it is time.",
          "raw_byte_range": [
            22855,
            22892
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "speaker",
          "speaker": "Ovelia",
          "text": "<SPEAKER>Ovelia<f8><e3>I'll not be much longer, Agrias.",
          "raw_byte_range": [
            22892,
            22937
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "speaker",
          "speaker": "Agrias",
          "text": "<SPEAKER>Agrias<f8><e3>Your escort has already arrived, Majesty.",
          "raw_byte_range": [
            22937,
            22991
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "speaker",
          "speaker": "Priest",
          "text": "<SPEAKER>Priest<f8><e3>Please, heed the good lady's words, Highness.<f8>You must hurry.",
          "raw_byte_range": [
            22991,
            23066
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "speaker",
          "speaker": "Swordsman",
          "text": "<SPEAKER>Swordsman<f8><e3>Still in here, are you? It's been<f8>the better part of an hour!",
          "raw_byte_range": [
            23066,
            23143
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "speaker": null,
          "text": "Gaffgarion, you forget yourself, ser!<f8>You are in the presence of the princess!",
          "raw_byte_range": [
            23143,
            23224
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "speaker",
          "speaker": "Gaffgarion",
          "text": "<SPEAKER>Gaffgarion<f8><e3>Mayhap bowed heads would less offend.<f8><f8>You would do well to waste less time on<f8>idle pleasantries.",
          "raw_byte_range": [
            23224,
            23337
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "speaker": null,
          "text": "I see even the noble Order of the<f8>Northern Sky cannot rid itself of<f8>vulgar knaves.",
          "raw_byte_range": [
            23337,
            23420
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "speaker": null,
          "text": "A guard captain in these rain-sodden<f8>hinterlands ought not expect chivalry.<f8><f8>We are in employ of the Order, not of it.<f8>Our pay does not cover trite courtesies<f8>to the likes of you.",
          "raw_byte_range": [
            23420,
            23602
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "speaker": null,
          "text": "Govern your tongue!",
          "raw_byte_range": [
            23602,
            23622
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "speaker": null,
          "text": "Enough. Let us be on our way.",
          "raw_byte_range": [
            23622,
            23652
          ]
        },
